\n<\N[5]>\F[62](\C[2]The monitor room \C[0] is located beyond
the door on the opposite side.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[4]]Um... Unfortunately, there is a thief among
us.

\n<Udo>\F[\V[4]]That thief sneaked into my collection room
and unbelievably stole Minato-chan's
(wax figure) bra.
\n<Sawa>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]Huh!?

\n<Udo>\F[\V[4]]Hey, didn't I say... that betrayal means an
immediate AV debut? It seems like
there's a girl among the three who wants
to debut.
\n<Udo>\FF[91]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]I wonder if the culprit is Kino-chan?
\n<Kino>\FF[91]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]...No, that's not true.
\n<Udo>\FF[91]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Hmmm?
\n<Udo>\FF[92]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Then maybe it's Momo-chan?
\n<Momo>\FF[92]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]No, that's not true~
\n<Udo>\FF[92]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Hmmm, hmmm.

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Then maybe it's Sawa-chan? Ah... by the way,
if the culprit doesn't come forward, all
three of you will debut together \I[12].
\n<Sawa>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]...I stole it.

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Hmmm... Just to be sure, should I ask for the
reason?

\n<Sawa>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]...B-because it was a design I liked, I wanted to
try wearing it...

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]I see! Attention, please! The culprit was
Sawa- chan~

\n<Kino>\FF[91]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]No, wait... There's no way Sawa would do
something like that...

\n<Momo>\FF[92]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]That's right~! There's no way Sawa would have
it~!

\n<Sawa>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]It's okay, both of you... I'm sorry... You
can punish me however you want...

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]That's disappointing... I thought you were a
smarter person, you know?

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Well then, as promised... you will make your
AV debut, \I[12]! Clap your hands~
\n<Kino & Momo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Kuh... Buu...
\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]\{ Shut up! \}
\n<Kino & Momo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]Eeeee...

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]...Sawa-chan, you're lucky. You've been saved~...
thanks to my genius inspiration♪
\n<Sawa>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[FF]What do you mean...

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]It's not so much that it fell from the sky
because my bra disappeared, but rather I
came up with a naughty event with
Minato-chan, you see~\I[12]

\n<Udo>\FF[93]\F[\V[4]]\AA[F]So, for this time only, by giving a
punishment, Sawa- chan's AV debut will
be avoided~!

... And so, as various emotions intertwine,
the night of the fourth day of the
training camp grew late.
